    {
      "sender_name": "Evan Larsen",
      "timestamp_ms": 1779731681177,
      "content": "You sent an attachment.",
      "share": {
        "link": "https://www.instagram.com/reel/DYwy9zANNw4/?id=3904845025908153400_30391476",
        "share_text": "FAMILY MEETING GUIDE below \u00f0\u009f\u0091\u0087\nBut first, proactive communication is a game changer for relationships.\n\nWe meet with couples every single day and many get caught in patterns of REACTIVE communication.\n\nReactive communication catches you guys off guard, can speak unnecessary conflicts, you don\u00e2\u0080\u0099t feel considered, and like you\u00e2\u0080\u0099re just not operating as a team.\n\nLook for ways to proactively communicate about:\n\u00e2\u0080\u00a2Plans, schedules, and looking ahead at the day, week, month \n\u00e2\u0080\u00a2Expectations so you\u00e2\u0080\u0099re on the same page and not making assumptions (like a trip)\n\u00e2\u0080\u00a2Your capacity (like where you\u00e2\u0080\u0099re at emotionally, mentally, physically so your partner knows)\n\u00e2\u0080\u00a2Needs in the relationship (talk about this before you\u00e2\u0080\u0099re in an argument)\n\u00e2\u0080\u00a2And even realizing that you\u00e2\u0080\u0099ve been off track and want to course-correct as a couple \n\nSome insider information: one very common thing we hear from women in sessions is how MUCH it would mean if her husband initiated these conversations. So even if you\u00e2\u0080\u0099re more reserved or go with the flow, look for ways you can BOTH initiate.\n\nWrite a \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00a5if this is helpful!\nWe have the best tool to implement this and make sure it happens:\n\nOur Family Meeting guide \u00f0\u009f\u0093\u0094\n\nIt provides you with time-efficient weekly, quarterly, and yearly templates that are proven to boost relationship satisfaction, prevent conflicts, and keep you on track as a couple!\n\nTwo ways to get it:\n\n1\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\u00e2\u0083\u00a3 The best way is included as a bonus gift in your welcome email for the 30-Day \u00e2\u0080\u0098Prioritizing Us\u00e2\u0080\u0099 Couples Challenge (our level 1 challenge). \nYou can sign-up for the next start date, and you get this guide immediately!\n\n>> Comment or DM the word CHALLENGE for this weblink!\n\u00e2\u0080\u00a6.and see why over 50,000 couples have loved these prompts! \n\n2\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\u00e2\u0083\u00a3 Or get The Family Meeting guide as a separate product itself!\n\n>> Comment or DM the word FAMILY for this weblink!\n\nThousands of couples use this and send us huge wins in their relationship!\nNow you try :)\n\nRooting for you two! \u00f0\u009f\u0099\u008f @meet_thefreemans",
        "original_content_owner": "meet_thefreemans"
      },
